data.description: **3% towards buyer's closing costs with acceptable offer, can be used for a rate by down** Bring on the space!! This 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home in Settlers Hammock is waiting for you! Tons of natural light welcomes you throughout this home. Large kitchen with GRANITE counters and ample cabinet space. Open floorpan allows for enjoyable entertaining. Relax on your back patio and take in the views from your Fully FENCED with plenty of space for kids and pets. Settlers Hammock has a community pool, playground and is conveniently located minutes to Kingsbay Naval Base, I-95, Jacksonville International Airport, shopping, beaches and more. This is the better than new home you have been looking for!
